WEBVTT

00:05:30.402 --> 00:05:33.000
It was 7 o'clock.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.876
By 8 o'clock, we kept on waiting,

00:05:35.876 --> 00:05:40.857
because it's not very uncommon 
that the leaders become late,

00:05:40.857 --> 00:05:42.539
for an hour or so.

00:05:43.239 --> 00:05:49.922
So after 8 o'clock, we took our bicycles
and went to these leaders' homes,

00:05:49.922 --> 00:05:52.278
just to remind them.

00:05:54.248 --> 00:05:58.945
One of the leader's wives told me,

00:05:58.945 --> 00:06:03.960
"Sorry, he is having some headache,
perhaps he cannot come."